--- !u!114 &870103344226331143
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 9083329293601777427}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9027c0af9529be34ba13ec95b152a9bd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 59a97d3656e9e96499618147032ae23d, type: 3}
  volume: 1
  canReplay: 0
  isIntroAudiotape: 1
  promptUnplayed: Blink to play recording
  promptPlaying: Playing...
  promptPlayed: Recording already heard
  rayDistance: 5
  gazeHitRadius: 0.5
  glowColor: {r: 0.55, g: 0.85, b: 1, a: 1}
  glowIntensity: 2.5
  pulseSpeed: 2.5
  playedGlowColor: {r: 0.35, g: 0.35, b: 0.35, a: 1}
  useStaticEffect: 1
  staticDuration: 0.55
  staticPeakAlpha: 0.65
  subtitleTexts:
  - If you're hearing this... you're still alive. That's more than I can say for
    most of us.
  - "This place \u2014 we called it the Facility. Endless corridors. No exits we
    could find. We didn't build it. We just... fell in."
  - "The anomalies started appearing three days after we arrived. We don't know what
    they are. They look almost human \u2014 until they move. They only move when
    you're not watching them. The moment you look away, they close in. Keep your
    eyes on them."
  - That's not a suggestion.
  - " But don't stare too long. Something happens to you. Your mind starts to \u2014
    [pause] fracture. We don't know why. If it gets bad, find a safe room. Lock the
    doors, stay inside. They won't follow you in. The corridors will go quiet. It's
    the only way to come back from it."
  - ' I scattered the access codes across this level deliberately. If you''re smart
    enough to survive long enough to find them all, you''re smart enough to do what
    needs to be done.'
  - "Sub-level B. There's a detonation room. We built it as a last resort \u2014
    to bring the whole thing down. Don't use it until you're sure you're ready."
  - Good luck.
  subtitleDurations:
  - 7
  - 11
  - 16
  - 2
  - 19
  - 7
